# thoth_browser_policy

Creates and updates browser policy objects.

## Example Usage

```terraform
resource "thoth_browser_policy" "chrome_lockdown" {
  name            = "Chrome Lockdown"
  provider        = "chrome"
  enforcement_mode = "enforce"
  active          = true

  policy_json = jsonencode({
    extension_settings = {
      "*" = {
        installation_mode = "blocked"
      }
    }
  })
}
```
